# ============================================
# WriteSpace - Environment Variables
# ============================================
# This is a static single-page application (SPA)
# that runs entirely in the browser.
#
# All data is persisted in localStorage — there
# is no backend server or external API required.
#
# No environment variables are needed to run
# this project. Simply install dependencies and
# start the dev server:
#
#   npm install
#   npm run dev
#
# ============================================

# If you ever need to add Vite-compatible
# environment variables in the future, prefix
# them with VITE_ so they are exposed to the
# client bundle via import.meta.env.VITE_*
#
# Example:
# VITE_APP_TITLE=WriteSpace
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com